title: Rais Sitdikov
text:
Rais Zinurovich Sitdikov (; born 30 November 1988) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He played 3 seasons in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Yenisey%20Krasnoyarsk">FC Yenisey Krasnoyarsk</a>.
